<H3> <TI>   Henan Meeting Held To Commend Model Workers </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Henan Meeting Held To Commend Model Workers </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   HK0205115494 Zhengzhou Henan People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 1030 GMT 27 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK0205115494 </F>
<F P=104>  Zhengzhou Henan People's Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Mandarin </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpts] The provincial meeting to commend model workers 
was held solemnly in the provincial people's hall on the morning 
of 27 April. [passage omitted] 
  Present were provincial leaders,including Li Changchun, Ren 
Keli, Song Zhaosu, Lin Yinghai, Wu Guangxian, Song Guochen, 
(Zhang Dehuang), Fan Qinchen, (Ma Jianzhang), Zhang Wenbin, (Hou 
Jingxu), Li Chengyu, Yu Jiahua, Liu Yujie, Tu Jiaju, Yao Ruxue, 
Mei Yangzheng, (Wang Quanshu), and (Lu Maosheng). [passage 
omitted] 
  Vice Governor Li Chengyu read out the decision of the Henan 
Provincial People's Government on commending model workers. 
[passage omitted] 
  After the namelist of model workers was read out, provincial 
leaders distributed awards to the representatives of model 
workers. One thousand model workers were cited at the meeting. 
[passage omitted] 
  Provincial party Secretary Li Changchun delivered an 
important speech. [passage omitted] 
  Li Changchun said: The provincial party committee and 
government called on the people throughout the province to learn 
from the model workers cited by the current meeting and from the 
advanced figures who have continuously emerged on every front of 
endeavor, base themselves on their jobs, learn from and catch up 
with the advanced, strive to achieve first-rate accomplishments, 
and make greater fresh contributions for new victories in this 
year's reform and modernization and for the realization of the 
magnificent goal of forging ahead in unity to rejuvenate Henan's 
economy. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

