<H3> <TI>   ARATS Secretary General Zou Zhekai Leaves Office </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    ARATS Secretary General Zou Zhekai Leaves Office </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   HK0305123394 Beijing ZHONGGUO XINWEN SHE in Chinese 1115 GMT 
3 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK0305123394 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing ZHONGGUO XINWEN SHE </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Report: "ARATS Confirms Secretary General Zou Zhekai Has </F>
Left Office"] 
  [Text] Beijing, 3 May (ZHONGGUO XINWEN SHE)--In a dispatch 
sent to Taiwan's Straits Exchange Foundation [SEF] today, the 
Association for Relations Across the Strait [ARATS] confirmed 
that ARATS Secretary General Zou Zhekai has already left office. 
  In the dispatch to the SEF, ARATS stated: Mr. Zhekai Zou is 
no longer secretary general of ARATS. He now works in XINHUA 
Hong Kong Branch. Zou Zhekai asked us, ARATS, to relay his 
gratitude to all the gentlemen of the SEF for their support for 
his work during his term of office as ARATS secretary general. 

</TEXT>

